  "3063720": {
    "name": "Monster Chef",
    "steam_appid": 3063720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/5149b9a8f90daea0e8456cf54ccd07af.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/5149b9a8f90daea0e8456cf54ccd07af.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在普兰佐的厨房，战场就是你的厨房！扮演一位厨师战士，捕猎怪物并用你的厨师武器现场烹饪它们。在这个类 Roguelike 砍杀游戏中，战斗可爱但凶猛的敌人，探索一个程序生成的世界，并建设你出色的客栈。提升你的烹饪技巧，发现意大利菜谱！磨砺你的刀锋，拿起盐瓶 - 晚餐已上桌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >把怪物变成美味佳肴</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/f809e8aa525dba7489fb5256407bedf0.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/f809e8aa525dba7489fb5256407bedf0.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你的厨师武器在战场上猎杀、战斗并烹饪怪物。在实时战斗中用香料调味，并通过快节奏的砍杀系统，将激烈的动作与高级料理完美融合，打造顶级美食。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >管理并重建你的旅馆</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/d1f8e3c13b8458883e2749e0f2afe7d1.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/d1f8e3c13b8458883e2749e0f2afe7d1.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成每日订单，招待来自精灵、兽人、 tritoni 和人类等奇幻部族的多元顾客，每位客人都有独特的口味和需求。升级你的旅馆，用华丽的家具装饰，将它从简陋小屋变成五星级的豪华酒馆！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>探索一个色彩缤纷的手绘世界</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/f31490d0fe574fdbc60701e8d1abfd68.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/f31490d0fe574fdbc60701e8d1abfd68.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索德丽西亚的不断变化的土地，这是一个具有程序生成地图的开放世界，每一天都带来新的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>揭开一个深刻的故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/477bf9e011169afc8cbdd8ff33d554fa.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/477bf9e011169afc8cbdd8ff33d554fa.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过击败巨大的首领，为德丽西亚的统治者准备盛大的盛宴。解锁新的生物群落，每个都充满了新怪物和挑战。结识一群多样化的角色，每个都有自己独特的故事和个性。与他们建立友谊，提供帮助，并通过独家对话揭开隐藏的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/818910a408e85e4fba7cdfaa24d788d8.poster.avif?t=1767107961\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063720/extras/818910a408e85e4fba7cdfaa24d788d8.webm?t=1767107961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
